graph TB
    subgraph "Developer Machine"
        IDE[IDE with OpenClaw]
        NPM[npm install nemoclaw]
    end

    subgraph "NemoClaw CLI (Installed Globally)"
        Binary[nemoclaw binary<br/>/usr/local/bin]
        Plugin[TypeScript Plugin<br/>nemoclaw/dist/]
        Blueprint[Python Blueprint<br/>nemoclaw-blueprint/]
    end

    subgraph "Docker Runtime"
        Gateway[OpenShell Gateway<br/>Container]
        Sandbox1[Sandbox: vllm<br/>Container]
        Sandbox2[Sandbox: nim<br/>Container]
        Sandbox3[Sandbox: nvidia<br/>Container]
    end

    subgraph "Inference Infrastructure"
        LocalNIM[Local NIM<br/>GPU Server]
        LocalvLLM[Local vLLM<br/>GPU Server]
        Cloud[NVIDIA Cloud<br/>build.nvidia.com]
    end

    subgraph "Persistent Storage"
        Config[~/.config/nemoclaw/<br/>credentials.json]
        State[~/.local/state/nemoclaw/<br/>sandbox-state.json]
        Logs[~/.local/share/nemoclaw/<br/>logs/]
    end

    IDE -->|Extends with| Plugin
    NPM -->|Installs| Binary
    Binary -->|Includes| Plugin
    Binary -->|Includes| Blueprint

    Binary -->|Manages| Gateway
    Gateway -->|Orchestrates| Sandbox1
    Gateway -->|Orchestrates| Sandbox2
    Gateway -->|Orchestrates| Sandbox3

    Sandbox1 -->|Routes to| LocalvLLM
    Sandbox2 -->|Routes to| LocalNIM
    Sandbox3 -->|Routes to| Cloud

    Binary -->|Reads/Writes| Config
    Gateway -->|Persists| State
    Gateway -->|Writes| Logs

    style Binary fill:#e1f5ff
    style Gateway fill:#e1ffe1
    style Cloud fill:#ffe1e1
    style Config fill:#fff4e1
